ry-specific details. The final part deals with the economic future of the region where the authors put forth a Latin American version of success. This book is a useful, in-depth introduction for students of Latin American economics as well as the general reader.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aEconomic developmentzLatin America. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economic History.2bisacsh  aEconomic growth.  aEconomic policy.  aEconomic reform.  aEconomics.  aLatin America.1 aSawyer, W. Charles, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2021z978311075072008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2021 Englishz978311075404908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2021z9783110753820oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831106749960 cprintz978311067490340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311067493440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110674934423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110674934/original  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  a978-3-11-075072-0  DG Ebook Package English 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075404-9  EBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12ST